= Appendix Exposé

An exposé for a thesis can range from 2 to 12 pages, depending on its type.
For our purposes, 2--3 pages (excluding the cover page) are sufficient.
Don't worry about the additional workload:
You can (re-)use almost everything from the exposé in the bachelor thesis itself.

